data.title: Missouri Valley Iowa Real Estate & Auctions - Country Homes, Farms, Land
data.meta_description: United Country Loess Hills Realty & Auction offers Missouri Valley Iowa real estate and auctions including country homes, farms, land, recreational property and commercial properties throughout Iowa and Nebraska.
data.text:
Serving Harrison, Pottawattamie, Shelby & Monona Counties

Also Serving Sarpy, Douglas, Washington & Burt Counties in Nebraska

Missouri Valley, Iowa is situated along the Loess Hills Scenic Byways and at the intersection of I-29 and U.S. Highway 30. The largest city in Harrison County is just 25 miles to the north of the Omaha Metropolitan Area, which also includes the city of Council Bluffs, Iowa. Missouri Valley has attractions and activities for all ages as well as excellent amenities and education.

Missouri Valley and the surrounding areas of Iowa offer an abundance of hunting and wildlife. Within Harrison County, Monona County and Pottawattamie County there are a combined 19 wildlife areas featuring ducks, geese, pheasants, deer, turkey and additional small game. Sawmill Hollow, Loess Hills Lavender Farm, Museum of Religious Arts, Wilson Island, Watson Steam Train and Wisecups Museum added to the attractiveness of Missouri Valley and Harrison County. United Country Loess Hills Realty & Auction offers real estate and auction services on residential, country estates, historic homes, farmland, recreational, hunting land and rural property for buyers and sellers. Our knowledgeable staff provides their expertise in four counties (Harrison, Pottawattamie, Shelby, Monona) in Iowa as well as Sarpy County, Douglas County, Washington County and Burt County in Nebraska.

United Country has achieved a top 1% Global Real Estate Franchise Ranking in the Franchise Business Review. As America’s largest integrated real estate and auction company specializing in lifestyle (non-urban) real estate we offer an unmatched marketing approach in selling or locating real estate. Local homes in town, luxury estates, development land and lots, bank foreclosures (REO) and non-urban commercial are only a few of the properties we have extensive experience with. Featuring a network in excess of 3,000 owned, top-ranked real estate and auction websites; United Country markets to a local, regional, national and worldwide audience. In addition, we are the only real estate company creating webpages for each of our client’s special property. These websites are discoverable by Google, advertised on hundreds of general and specialty sites and are posted on websites found on the first page of a Google search.

Relocating, retirement or vacation getaway or retreat, allow the experts to make the process stress free and successful. United Country Loess Hills Realty & Auction will meet and exceed your expectations with the finest selection of residential, recreational and rural properties in the surrounding eight-county region. We look forward to working with you soon.
